2 CONT Birth:  1716 
2 CONT Death:  Mar. 10, 1791 
2 CONT Here lies the body of the Rev. John Cuthbertson, who after a labour of about 40 years in the ministry of the Gospel among the disenting Covenanters of America, departed this life 10th March, 1791 in the 75 year of his age.
2 CONT 
